  "detailed_description": "1026年，世界第一大国翠纳在仙草战争的洗礼后，政权分裂，各城区由各大城主统治，内忧外患的国情下，佣兵一跃成为了世界的主流职业。你可以心怀正义，为世界和平而努力；也可以唯利是图，游走于各大势力中间。你可以得到一切你想要的东西，强大的武器和装备，甚至各城主的小秘密，各色美女和金钱。铸造和平，统一世界，等你掌控！<br><br>游戏特色：<br>■六章风格不同的大陆地图，每张地图都有属于自己的故事。<br><br>■动态的世界，要塞可能随时被叛乱的佣兵攻打，是坐视不管，还是出手相救由你决定。<br><br>■硬核游戏，如果队员在战斗中死亡，你将永久失去他。<br><br>■努力发掘最有潜力的佣兵，将他们培养成你需要的人。当然越是强力的佣兵培养起来越是困难。<br><br>■通过各种赚钱方法维持佣兵团运作，贸易、夺回、攻打、演出等等。付不出工资佣兵可是会离你而去的。<br>官方QQ群：473017965。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196620/extras/3d1e768b3ad1aeb502628bcff5e5ea42.avif?t=1580276013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196620/extras_big/3d1e768b3ad1aeb502628bcff5e5ea42.avif?t=1580276013 width=800 height=450 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196620/extras/37473d1e29992db1a1fca8e37e74d0a9.avif?t=1580276013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196620/extras_big/37473d1e29992db1a1fca8e37e74d0a9.avif?t=1580276013 width=800 height=450 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196620/extras/68e21917daf1e69aaf3fc432f6835cd9.avif?t=1580276013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196620/extras_big/68e21917daf1e69aaf3fc432f6835cd9.avif?t=1580276013 width=800 height=450 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196620/extras/c0a87504e09bf05e4207e190d8491a20.avif?t=1580276013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1196620/extras_big/c0a87504e09bf05e4207e190d8491a20.avif?t=1580276013 width=800 height=448 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https